text: The Immanuel Church () is a church building at the street of Oxtorgsgatan in the town of Jönköping in Sweden. It belongs to the Uniting Church in Sweden. The church was built in 1975. It was opened in 1976. ==References== ==Other websites== *official website Category:Churches in Sweden Category:Buildings and structures in Jönköping
